<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Blog | Siddharth Dutt — AI Transformation & IT Operations</title>
<meta name="description" content="Insights on AIOps, GenAI, ITSM automation, and AI-driven service delivery by Siddharth Dutt — Senior IT Operations Leader.">
<meta name="author" content="Siddharth Dutt">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://duttsiddharth.github.io/sid/blog.html">

<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:title" content="AI Blog | Siddharth Dutt">
<meta property="og:description" content="Insights on AIOps, GenAI, ITSM automation, and AI-driven service delivery.">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://duttsiddharth.github.io/sid/blog.html">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #0d0d0d;
    --paper: #f5f0e8;
    --cream: #ede7d6;
    --rust: #c0440a;
    --gold: #b8922a;
    --muted: #6b6258;
    --line: rgba(13,13,13,0.12);
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--paper); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--rust); }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--rust); letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1.6rem; }
  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--rust); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .blog-hero {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 9rem 6rem 5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .blog-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; right: -80px; top: -80px;
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(192,68,10,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .blog-hero::after {
    content: '// AI·Blog';
    position: absolute; right: 6rem; bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9rem);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.03);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    pointer-events: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s forwards;
  }
  .blog-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--paper);
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s forwards;
  }
  .blog-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rust); }
  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 1.2rem; max-width: 520px;
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s forwards;
  }

  /* ── FILTER BAR ── */
  .filter-bar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 2rem 6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s forwards;
  }
  .filter-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }
  .filter-btn {
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line); background: transparent;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .filter-btn:hover, .filter-btn.active {
    border-color: var(--rust); color: var(--rust); background: rgba(192,68,10,0.05);
  }

  /* ── BLOG GRID ── */
  .blog-main {
    padding: 4rem 6rem 6rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(360px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  /* ── POST CARD ── */
  .post-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .post-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .post-card:hover { box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--rust); transform: translate(-3px,-3px); }

  .post-card-top {
    background: var(--ink); padding: 2rem 2rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 160px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
  }
  .post-card-top::before {
    content: attr(data-icon);
    position: absolute; right: 1.5rem; top: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 2.5rem; opacity: 0.18;
  }
  .post-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .post-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.35rem; line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .post-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rust); }

  .post-card-body { padding: 1.8rem 2rem; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .post-excerpt { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; flex: 1; }

  .post-meta {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .post-date { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .post-read {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--rust); letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
    background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0;
  }
  .post-card:hover .post-read { gap: 0.75rem; }

  /* ── FEATURED CARD ── */
  .post-card.featured {
    grid-column: span 2;
    flex-direction: row;
  }
  .post-card.featured .post-card-top {
    width: 45%; min-height: 240px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .post-card.featured .post-card-body { padding: 2.5rem; }
  .post-card.featured .post-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .post-card.featured .post-excerpt { font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* ── COMING SOON CARD ── */
  .post-card.coming-soon {
    border-style: dashed; opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .post-card.coming-soon .post-card-top { background: var(--cream); }
  .coming-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); text-align: center; padding: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── ARTICLE MODAL ── */
  .modal-backdrop {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 200;
    background: rgba(13,13,13,0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.35s ease;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .modal-backdrop.open {
    opacity: 1; pointer-events: all;
  }

  .modal-panel {
    background: var(--paper);
    max-width: 760px; width: 100%;
    margin: auto;
    position: relative;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
    min-height: 60vh;
  }
  .modal-backdrop.open .modal-panel {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .modal-close {
    position: absolute; top: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--ink); border: none;
    color: var(--paper); width: 40px; height: 40px;
    font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    z-index: 10; transition: background 0.2s;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }
  .modal-close:hover { background: var(--rust); }

  .modal-header {
    background: var(--ink); padding: 3.5rem 3rem 2.5rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .modal-header::before {
    content: attr(data-icon);
    position: absolute; right: 2.5rem; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 7rem; opacity: 0.06;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .modal-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .modal-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .modal-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rust); }
  .modal-byline {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45); letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .modal-byline span { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65); }

  .modal-body {
    padding: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.85; color: #2a2420;
  }
  .modal-body h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.45rem; color: var(--ink);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .modal-body h3 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust); margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .modal-body p { margin-bottom: 1.3rem; }
  .modal-body ul, .modal-body ol {
    padding-left: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
  }
  .modal-body li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .modal-body blockquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--cream);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .modal-body .callout {
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--rust);
  }
  .modal-body .callout strong {
    display: block; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .modal-body .callout p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.8); line-height: 1.7; }
  .modal-body .stat-row {
    display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .modal-body .stat-box {
    flex: 1; min-width: 120px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .modal-body .stat-box .num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--rust); line-height: 1;
  }
  .modal-body .stat-box .lbl {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .modal-body hr {
    border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }
  .modal-body code {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.82rem;
    background: var(--cream); padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .modal-footer {
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .modal-author {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .modal-author strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .modal-close-btn {
    padding: 0.7rem 1.8rem; background: var(--ink);
    border: none; color: var(--paper);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .modal-close-btn:hover { background: var(--rust); }

  /* ── NEWSLETTER STRIP ── */
  .newsletter-strip {
    background: var(--rust); padding: 3rem 6rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .newsletter-text h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .newsletter-text p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7); }
  .newsletter-input-group { display: flex; gap: 0; }
  .newsletter-input {
    padding: 0.85rem 1.4rem;
    border: none; background: rgba(245,240,232,0.15);
    color: var(--paper); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.82rem;
    width: 260px; outline: none;
  }
  .newsletter-input::placeholder { color: rgba(245,240,232,0.4); }
  .newsletter-btn {
    padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem; border: none;
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .newsletter-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink); color: rgba(245,240,232,0.35);
    padding: 2rem 6rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--rust); text-decoration: none; }
  footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.2rem; }
    .blog-hero { padding: 8rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .filter-bar { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .blog-main { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .post-card.featured { flex-direction: column; grid-column: span 1; }
    .post-card.featured .post-card-top { width: 100%; }
    .newsletter-strip { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
    .newsletter-input { width: 100%; }
    footer { padding: 1.5rem; flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .modal-body { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .modal-header { padding: 3rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
    .modal-footer { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">S. Dutt</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="index.html#summary">About</a>
    <a href="index.html#services">Services</a>
    <a href="case-studies.html">Case Studies</a>
    <a href="index.html#ai-projects">Projects</a>
    <a href="blog.html" class="active">AI Blog</a>
    <a href="assessment.html" style="color:var(--rust);">Free Assessment</a>
    <a href="index.html#contact">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="blog-hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">// Perspectives &amp; Insights</div>
  <h1>The <em>AI</em> Operations<br>Intelligence Brief</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Practical thinking on AIOps, GenAI in service delivery, ITSM automation, and the future of intelligent IT operations — from 20+ years on the frontline.</p>
</div>

<!-- FILTER BAR -->
<div class="filter-bar">
  <span class="filter-label">Filter:</span>
  <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="aiops">AIOps</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="genai">GenAI</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="itsm">ITSM</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="automation">Automation</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="leadership">Leadership</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="servicenow">ServiceNow</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="itil">ITIL</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="managed-services">Managed Services</button>
</div>

<!-- BLOG GRID -->
<main class="blog-main" id="blog-grid">

  <!-- FEATURED POST -->
  <article class="post-card featured" data-category="aiops genai" data-post="1">
    <div class="post-card-top" data-icon="🤖">
      <div class="post-tag">✦ Featured · AIOps · GenAI</div>
      <div class="post-title">Why <em>AIOps</em> is Not Just<br>Another Buzzword</div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <p class="post-excerpt">
        After two decades in IT operations, I've watched trends come and go. AIOps is different. When implemented correctly — with real telemetry, real workflows, and real ITIL alignment — it doesn't just monitor your infrastructure. It anticipates failure, auto-routes incidents, and learns from every resolution.
      </p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">Jun 2026 · 8 min read</span>
        <button class="post-read" data-post="1">Read Article →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- POST 2 -->
  <article class="post-card" data-category="genai itsm" data-post="2">
    <div class="post-card-top" data-icon="⚡">
      <div class="post-tag">GenAI · ITSM</div>
      <div class="post-title">Prompt Engineering<br>for <em>ITSM Teams</em></div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <p class="post-excerpt">Most service desk teams are sitting on untapped potential. With the right prompt architecture, Claude or ChatGPT can triage tickets, generate incident summaries, draft RCA reports, and coach L1 agents — all without replacing your team.</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">May 2026 · 6 min read</span>
        <button class="post-read" data-post="2">Read →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- POST 3 -->
  <article class="post-card" data-category="automation" data-post="3">
    <div class="post-card-top" data-icon="🔗">
      <div class="post-tag">Automation · n8n</div>
      <div class="post-title"><em>n8n</em> + Claude:<br>The ITSM Power Combo</div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <p class="post-excerpt">How I built SmartDesk — an AI triage system that auto-classifies 42% of tickets — using n8n workflows and Claude API. A complete walkthrough of the architecture, prompt design, and lessons learned.</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">Apr 2026 · 10 min read</span>
        <button class="post-read" data-post="3">Read →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- POST 4 -->
  <article class="post-card" data-category="leadership aiops" data-post="4">
    <div class="post-card-top" data-icon="📊">
      <div class="post-tag">Leadership · Strategy</div>
      <div class="post-title">The AI Adoption<br><em>Maturity Model</em> for IT</div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <p class="post-excerpt">Not all organisations are ready for the same AI interventions. This maturity framework helps CIOs and service delivery leaders identify where they are — and what their next AI investment should be.</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">Mar 2026 · 7 min read</span>
        <button class="post-read" data-post="4">Read →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- POST 5 -->
  <article class="post-card" data-category="itsm" data-post="5">
    <div class="post-card-top" data-icon="📋">
      <div class="post-tag">ITSM · ITIL</div>
      <div class="post-title">ITIL 4 Meets<br><em>Generative AI</em></div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <p class="post-excerpt">ITIL 4's Service Value System wasn't designed with LLMs in mind — but its flexibility makes it ideal for AI augmentation. A practical guide to overlaying GenAI capabilities on your existing ITIL framework.</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">Feb 2026 · 5 min read</span>
        <button class="post-read" data-post="5">Read →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- POST 6 -->
  <article class="post-card" data-category="genai automation" data-post="6">
    <div class="post-card-top" data-icon="🧠">
      <div class="post-tag">GenAI · RAG</div>
      <div class="post-title">RAG for <em>Knowledge</em><br>Base Automation</div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <p class="post-excerpt">Retrieval-Augmented Generation can turn your ServiceNow knowledge base into an intelligent self-service engine. Here's the architecture I recommend for enterprise ITSM knowledge automation.</p>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">Jan 2026 · 9 min read</span>
